Question as on 28 Sept

1) Apply adaptive local noise reduction filter

2) Apply adaptive median filter

3) Perform inverse filtering on a given image

4) Perform homomorphic filtering on a given image

5) Suppose that a digital image is subject to histogram equalisation. Show that the second pass of histogram equalisation is same as the first pass

6) Let the two image f(x,y) and g(x,y) have histogram h(f) and h(g). Show the result for the following arithmetic operations between two histograms

	f(x,y) + g(x,y)
	f(x,y) - g(x,y)
	h(f) + h(g)
	h(f) - h(g) 
